               Arguments ZLIB and JPEG for codecs using ZLib and Jpeg.

0.4betadev6:
    * Correg.: Display bug with ZRle codec in 32-bits modes only.
    * Ańadido: Gradient mode support in codec Tight for 16 and 32-bits depths.

0.4betadev5:
    * Ańadido: Added an option in socket to prevent packet buffering.

